00:54:10.790 --> 00:54:12.620
going on within the village.

00:54:12.620 --> 00:54:16.580
So it's as if almost
complete markets there.

00:54:16.580 --> 00:54:22.420
Then you village-level risk,
which is aggregate risk.

00:54:22.420 --> 00:54:25.660
And then someone comes
in ostensibly trying

00:54:25.660 --> 00:54:28.390
to insure that aggregate risk.

00:54:28.390 --> 00:54:30.730
So you would think, oh great,
