00:58:53.960 --> 00:58:57.020
essentially what this
thing turns out to be

00:58:57.020 --> 00:59:00.680
is household i's risk
tolerance times the sum

00:59:00.680 --> 00:59:06.200
of the risk toleri of the other
households in the village.

00:59:06.200 --> 00:59:08.090
But hopefully you're
getting some intuition

00:59:08.090 --> 00:59:12.515
for where we're getting
the risk aversion measures.

00:59:17.850 --> 00:59:21.590
This, I think, you
